=== DESIRED ===
await run.timeTravel({ step: "counter", iteration: 2 })
```

## Summary

- `snapshot.context.counter` only has iteration 4 (the last one)
- `metadata.iterationCount` tells us there were 4 iterations, but we can't access iterations 1-3
- To time-travel to iteration 2, we must manually use `setState()` workaround + reconstruct state
- **Request**: Store all iterations so `timeTravel({ step, iteration: N })` just works

